|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 16|de|June 16|ja|June 16|zh|June 16|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hirose Sahei|de|広瀬宰平|ja|広瀬宰平|zh|広瀬宰平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a businessperson (died [[1914]]). * {{ill|Bunka|ja|文政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1829|de|1829|ja|1829|zh|1829|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|June 6|de|June 6|ja|June 6|zh|June 6|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Honinbō Shūsaku|de|本因坊秀策|ja|本因坊秀策|zh|本因坊秀策|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a professional Go player (died [[1862]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gr