{{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 5''' is the 5th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Gendoku|de|元徳|ja|元徳|zh|元徳|qq=}} 3rd year / {{ill|Genkō|de|元弘|ja|元弘|zh|元弘|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1331|de|1331|ja|1331|zh|1331|qq=}} {{ill|June 10|de|June 10|ja|June 10|zh|June 10|qq=}}) – In the rebellion known as {{ill|Genkō no Ran|de|元弘の乱|ja|元弘の乱|zh|元弘の乱|qq=}}, the reattempted anti-bakufu plot of Emperor {{ill|Go-Daigo|de|後醍醐天皇|ja|後醍醐天皇|zh|後醍醐天皇|qq=}} was leaked to the Ashikaga Shogunate, resulting in the arrest of figures such as {{ill|Hino Toshiki|de|日野俊基|ja|日野俊基|zh|日野俊基|qq=}}. The emperor then took refuge on 【Oki Province†Oki_Province】. * {{ill|Genna|de|Genna|ja|元和|zh|Genna|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=}} {{ill|1615|de|1615|ja|1615|zh|1615|qq=}} {{ill|June 1|de|June 1|ja|June 1|zh|June 1|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|de|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|zh|Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}} set out from Kyoto (from Nijō Castle) in preparation for the summer siege of Osaka. * {{ill|Tenmei|de|Tenmei|ja|天保|zh|Tenmei|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=}} {{ill|1786|de|1786|ja|1786|zh|1786|qq=}} June 1) – Under orders from the Tokugawa shogunate, the official {{ill|Mogami Tokunai|de|最上徳内|ja|最上徳内|zh|最上徳内|qq=}} landed on Ezo (specifically, on Etoroshima, also known as Etoroshima in Oki Province). == Births == * {{ill|Jōgan|de|Jōgan|ja|Jōgan|zh|Jōgan|qq=}} 9th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|de|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|zh|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|867|de|867|ja|867|zh|867|qq=}} {{ill|June 10|de|June 10|ja|June 10|zh|June 10|qq=}}) – {{ill|Uta Tennō|de|宇