aryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=}} {{ill|1829|de|1829|ja|1829|zh|1829|qq=}} {{ill|June 6|de|June 6|ja|June 6|zh|June 6|qq=}}) – {{ill|Honinbō Shūsaku|de|本因坊秀策|ja|本因坊秀策|zh|本因坊秀策|qq=}}, a professional Go player (died [[1862]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=}} {{ill|1835|de|1835|ja|1835|zh|1835|qq=}} {{ill|May 31|de|May 31|ja|May 31|zh|May 31|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hijikata Toshizō|de|土方歳三|ja|土方歳三|zh|土方歳三|qq=}}, vice-commander of the Shinsengumi (died [[1869]]). == Deaths == * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=}} {{ill|1680|de|1680|ja|1680|zh|1680|qq=}} {{ill|June 1|de|June 1|ja|June 1|zh|June 1|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hayashi Gahō|de|林鵞峰|ja|林鵞峰|zh|林鵞峰|qq=}} (Shunsai), a Zhu Xi scholar and son of Hayashi Rinsan (born {{ill|1618|de|1618|ja|1618|zh|1618|qq=}}). * {{ill|Genji|ja|元治|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=}} {{ill|1864|de|1864|ja|1864|zh|1864|qq=}} {{ill|June 8|de|June 8|ja|June 8|zh|June 8|qq=}}) – {{ill|Reisui Iguyasu|de|冷泉為恭|ja|冷泉為恭|zh|冷泉為恭|qq=}}, an imperial court painter. == Commemorations == * {{ill|Duanwu|de|Duanwu|ja|端午|1=Dragon Boat Festival|2=ja|3=端午|4=fr|5=Festival des bateaux-dragons|6=ru|7=Праздник драконьих лодок|8=es|9=Fiesta del Barco del Dragón|10=nl|11=Drakenbootfeest|zh|端午|1=Dragon Boat Festival|2=ja|3=端午|4=fr|5=Festival des bateau