endar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1864|de|1864|ja|1864|zh|1864|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|June 8|de|June 8|ja|June 8|zh|June 8|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Reisui Iguyasu|de|冷泉為恭|ja|冷泉為恭|zh|冷泉為恭|qq=|qq=draft}}, an imperial court painter. == Commemorations == * {{ill|Duanwu|de|Duanwu|ja|端午|1=Dragon Boat Festival|2=ja|3=端午|4=fr|5=Festival des bateaux-dragons|6=ru|7=Праздник драконьих лодок|8=es|9=Fiesta del Barco del Dragón|10=nl|11=Drakenbootfeest|zh|端午|1=Dragon Boat Festival|2=ja|3=端午|4=fr|5=Festival des bateaux-dragons|6=ru|7=Праздник драконьих лодок|8=es|9=Fiesta del Barco del Dragón|10=nl|11=Drakenbootfeest|qq=|qq=draft}} – The Dragon Boat Festival is celebrated. * Duanwu Festival (端午節) is observed in Taiwan. <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://jp.taiwantoday.tw/news.php?unit=151&post=115869|title=TAIWAN TODAY日本語版からのお知らせ|publisher=Taiwan Today|accessdate=2017-05-26|qq=}}</ref>
