égorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1829|de|1829|ja|1829|zh|1829|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1829|qq=}} {{ill|June 6|de|June 6|ja|June 6|zh|June 6|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 6|qq=}}) – [[:en:Hon'inbō Shūsaku|Honinbō Shūsaku]], a professional Go player (died [[1862]]). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1835|de|1835|ja|1835|zh|1835|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1835|qq=}} {{ill|May 31|de|May 31|ja|May 31|zh|May 31|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 31|qq=}}) – [[:en:Hijikata Toshizō|Hijikata Toshizō]], vice-commander of the Shinsengumi (died [[1869]]). == Deaths == * [[:en:Enpō|Enpō]] 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1680|de|1680|ja|1680|zh|1680|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1680|qq=}} {{ill|June 1|de|June 1|ja|June 1|zh|June 1|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 1|qq=}}) – [[:en:Hayashi Gahō|Hayashi Gahō]] (Shunsai), a Zhu Xi scholar and son of Hayashi Rinsan (born {{ill|1618|de|1618|ja|1618|zh|1618|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1618|qq=}}). * [[:en:Genji era|Genji]] 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|de|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|zh|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1864|de|1864|ja|1864|zh|1864|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1864|qq=}} {{ill|June 8|de|June 8|ja|June 8|zh|June 8|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 8|qq=}}) – [[:en:Reizei Tamechika|Reisui Iguyasu]], an imperial court painter. == Commemorations == * [[:en:Dragon Boat Festival|Dragon Boat Festival]] – The Dragon Boat Festival is celebrated. * Duanwu Festival (端午節) is observed in Taiwan. <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://jp.taiwantoday.tw/news.php?unit=151&post=115869|title=TAIWAN TODAY日本語版からのお知らせ|publisher=Taiwan Today|accessdate=2017-05-26|qq=}}</ref>
